title: Readout of the Vice President's Meeting with Prime Minister Vlad Filat of Moldova | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Vice President


For Immediate Release
January 21, 2010

 



Readout of the Vice President's Meeting with Prime Minister Vlad Filat of Moldova




The Vice President met Moldovan Prime Minister Vlad Filat on January 20, 2010.Â  The Vice President commended Prime Minister Filat for his efforts to bring Moldova closer to the European Union, improve relations with its neighbors, and attract foreign investment.
